Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統剛剛走進司法部大樓\NThe Vice President just entered the Department of Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現場請到的是艾拉·薩伊德\NWe're here with Ayla Sayyad,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她發表在《華爾街電訊報》上的文章\Nwhose Wall Street Telegraph article
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接促成了這次調查  艾拉\Ncatalyzed the investigation. Ayla.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.47,0:00:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵問題在於白宮與此事是否有牽連\NThe issue at stake is whether the White House was in any way involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是否有國外資金用於換取政治支持\NWas foreign money traded for political favors?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是否對外交關係產生影響\NDid it influence diplomatic relations?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,單是為來自中國的政治獻金洗白就是違法的\NJust the act of laundering Chinese contributions is illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這筆錢對白宮決策產生影響的話\NIf it had a significant impact on White House policy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是更嚴重的罪行了\Nthat's a far more serious crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.91,0:00:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾多次與丹尼爾·拉尼根會面\NYou've met with Daniel Lanagin on multiple occasions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  2003年起我們曾11次共處一室\NWe were in the same room, yes, on 11 occasions since 2003.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其中我們交談過的只有三次\NBut we only spoke on three of those occasions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那幾次已經標出來了\NThose instances are highlighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.71,0:00:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們談了什麼\NWhat did you discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那都是在籌款會上\NWell, these were fundraisers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對著幾十號人發表講話\NI speak to dozens of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.76,0:01:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有什麼特定的話題\Nusually about nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.39,0:01:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是南方人  鄧巴女士\NI'm southern, Ms. Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.74,0:01:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我媽媽教導我\NMy mother taught me that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,席間講話不僅禮貌\Nconversation during mealtime is not only polite,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.37,0:01:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有助消化\Nit aids the digestive process.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你沒有跟他談到過\NSo you didn't speak to him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿道希部落向這些超級政治行動委員會捐款的事嗎\Nabout the Adohi tribe's contributions to any of these super PACs?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒有\NAbsolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從不和支持者提超級政治行動委員會\NI never discuss super PACs with any supporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們熟悉法律規定\NWe both know the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這些禮節性的談話中\NDuring one of these polite conversations,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉尼根先生可曾向你提起過馮山德\Ndo you recall Mr. Lanagin ever mentioning Xander Feng?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.33,0:01:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想沒有\NI do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.14,0:01:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說過這個名字嗎\NDoes that name mean anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說除了鋪天蓋地的媒體報道嗎\NOther than being plastered all over the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這個角度說  就像我也聽說過金·卡戴珊\NIn that regard it means as much as Kim Kardashian.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我再說得明確些\NThen let me be more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對馮先生的政治活動有什麼瞭解\NWhat knowledge do you have of Mr. Feng's political activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是你丈夫的意思還是\NIs this coming from your husband, or is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的意思\NFrom me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且不是說我不再支持法案了\NAnd it's not that I don't support the bill anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是採訪的事\NIt's just the article.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經答應讓馬特做專訪了\NWe've promised Matt an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:01:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那往後推幾周吧\NMaybe in a few weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.17,0:02:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等調查塵埃落定之後再說\Nonce the investigation has died down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《紐約時代雜誌》可不會乾等著我們\NThe New York Times isn't going to wait for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.21,0:02:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經騰出十月份的封面\NThey've already scheduled the cover for October.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鑒於我們的安排\NBased on our timing --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就恕難參與了\NThen I can't be a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為嘉樂威的事  是不是\NIt's the Galloway nonsense, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾  別這麼說\NClaire, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你直說就行  我們是朋友\NYou can say so. We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確影響不好\NIt doesn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不會真相信我\NYou don't actually believe I --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不信\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但國內還是有不少人信的\NBut enough of the country still does.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加勒特現在需要爭取每一份支持\NAnd Garrett needs every bit of support he can get right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你心意已決了\NSo there's no convincing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡可能幫你\NI'll help as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄地幫\NQuietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有傳言說你和馮先生\NThere are rumors that you and Mr. Feng
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在去年五月的貿易峰會上進行了私下接觸\Nserved as back channels to the trade summit last May.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  就是"傳言"\NExactly. Rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.17,0:02:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,峰會期間馮就在美國境內\NWe have Feng in the U.S. during the summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算他做了私下接觸\NWell, if he was back-channeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我知情\Nand even if I were aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種外交接觸一般都是保密的\Nany form of diplomatic communication is usually classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和總統說起過馮嗎\NHave you ever discussed Feng with the President?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:03:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北京每一個權勢人物我們都會說起\NAny major player in Beijing is worthy of discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是承認了\NSo that's a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是陳述一般情況\NIt's a general comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.23,0:03:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在能源危機期間與別人說起過他嗎\NDid you discuss him during the energy crisis?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你是指跟他合資投資精煉廠的\NI assuming you're alluding to the refinery co-venture with --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我是指雷蒙德·塔斯克\NYes. With Raymond Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們從來沒聊起過精煉廠\NThe refinery was never part of our conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要的是能立即見效的方案\NWe needed an immediate solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建精煉廠在短期內什麼都解決不了\NA refinery would have solved nothing in the short term.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且據我所知  這交易最後黃了\NAnd it's my understanding that deal fell through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  但塔斯克拿到了補貼\NCorrect. But Tusk did receive a subsidy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他核電供應商也都拿到了\NAs did every other nuclear energy provider.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他和馮有聯繫\NBut his connection with Feng,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有釤補貼\Nthen a subsidy on samarium --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人從這筆補貼中獲利\NNobody made any profits off these subsidies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至多也就是保本而已\NAt best they were breaking even.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實上  雷蒙德一開始還反對補貼的事\NIn fact, Raymond fought us on the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們再說說傑斐遜港大橋吧\NThen let's back up to the Port Jefferson Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也怨不得她  這的確值得擔憂\NI don't blame her. It's a valid concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他我不會談嘉樂威的事\NTell him I won't engage on Galloway,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以乾脆也別問\Nso there's no point in asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是馬特·貝\NThis is Matt Bai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要問什麼我們說了不算  而他肯定會問這個\NWe can't dictate what he'll ask. And he will ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就說我不會回應這些無聊八卦\NWell, then I'll just say I won't answer tabloid questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是個合理的問題\NIt's a legitimate question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醜聞對選舉有什麼影響\NHow the scandal could affect the vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我建議我們也不做了\NLook, I say you pull out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,取消掉整篇專題\NWe scrap the whole piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑姬在和我們對著干\NJackie is fighting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統方面又指望不上\NThe leadership is noncommittal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要這篇專訪讓大家重新關注法案\NWe need this article to refocus attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這於你不利啊\NBut it'll hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對你的形象和法案都不利\NBoth your personal image and the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我們誰都不靠\NBut if we cut the cord,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約好的兩場採訪\Nwe schedule two interviews,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼取消了  馬特不會生氣嗎\Nthen we cancel, won't Matt be furious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家只會看到我們的退縮\NThe story will be about pulling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要權衡利弊\NWe're talking about the lesser of two evils.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望你成為目標\NI don't want you to become the target,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-使我們的努力白費  -如果不是我去呢\N- to undo all the work - Then what if it's not me at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可你說第一夫人不打算\NBut you said the first lady wasn't going --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是她  是其他人\NNot her. Someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建設大橋是否是換取切斷共和黨資助金的籌碼\NWas the bridge a trade-off to prevent additional GOP funding?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據我所知\NAs far as I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這座大橋是總統在兌現\Nthe bridge was a delivery on a promise
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他對選民做出的承諾\Nthe president had made to the voters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒問完嗎\NAre we finished here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快了\NAlmost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會見過多少位國會議員  鄧巴女士\NHow many members of Congress have you interviewed, Ms. Dunbar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,200嗎\NAbout 200?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,194位\N194.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想幫忙\NWell, I want to be of help,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我想前面194位都已經說得差不多了\Nbut I doubt I can offer any more than the 194 that preceded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得到了一些有用的證詞\NI have gotten some useful testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-從誰那兒  -眾議院高層\N- From who? - A high-ranking House member.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領導層的嗎\NIn the leadership?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能說\NI'm not at liberty to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮑勃·博奇  傑姬·夏普\NBob Birch? Jackie Sharp?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人說他參加了7月14日\NThis individual says he attended a meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在總統辦公室的會議\NJuly 14th in the Oval Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說是個男的  那麼一定是博奇\NShe said "He," so it must have been Birch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德肯定能輕易收買他\NI'm sure Raymond had no trouble buying him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也參加了那次會議\NYou attended that meeting also.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是這樣的\NIt appears so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得那次會議的主題嗎\NDo you recall the subject of that meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一波共和黨的攻擊廣告\NA wave of conservative attack ads.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有足夠財力與之抗衡\NWe were being outspent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定很震驚吧\NIt must have been quite a shock
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉尼根轉而把錢捐給了另一黨派\Nwhen Lanagin's tribe shifted contributions to the other party,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前他們從沒給共和黨捐過錢\Nwhen they hadn't given a single dime to the Republicans before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這的確會令我們震驚\NWell, it would have been a shock,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們當時並不知道錢是哪來的\Nbut we didn't know where the money was coming from at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:06:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據我的線人說\NAccording to my source...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮑勃·博奇\NBob Birch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的線人說  當時預計有兩千五百萬\NMy source says the estimate was 25 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引用你說的話\NYou said, and I quote,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"憑空出現這麼多錢\N"With this kind of influx,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有人違規了"\Nyou can be sure somebody isn't playing by the rules."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是我說過的話\NSounds like something I might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮑勃的記性比我好\NBob has a better memory than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑斐遜港大橋剛獲批\NThe money stopped just after
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.98,0:07:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這筆錢就中斷了\Nthe Port Jefferson Bridge was approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是真有想法\NIs there a theory here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是查不出頭緒就瞎猜\Nor are you just grasping at straws?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大橋與馮有關\NThe bridge leads to Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馮與拉尼根和塔斯克有關\NFeng gives me Lanagin and Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克和總統\NTusk and the president --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鄧巴女士  你想玩六度分隔的話\NMs. Dunbar, you want to play six degrees of separation,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能扯上吉米·霍法和教皇\Nyou could throw in Jimmy Hoffa and the pope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}82年神秘失蹤的工會領袖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼一度分隔如何\NThen how about one degree of separation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格拉斯·斯坦普  你的幕僚長\NDouglas Stamper, your chief of staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是7月14日他在拉尼根的賭場\NThis is him at Lanagin's casino July 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我用這些申請了搜查證  調出了飛行記錄\NI used these to get a warrant for flight records.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  斯坦普先生飛去北京\NThe next day, Mr. Stamper was on a flight to Beijing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他為什麼去賭場\NWhy was he at the casino?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼去北京\NAnd why was he in Beijing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想與委託人談談\NI would like to speak to my client.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請吧\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力\NI work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不拖泥帶水  我知道重要的是什麼\NI keep things simple. I know what my priorities are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是有這麼個人\NBut there's this -- this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不在我的生活中  而是在我生活的邊緣\NShe's not even in my life, except on the edges,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以界限很模糊\Nmaking things blurrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這並不讓我想喝酒\NIt doesn't tempt me to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那感覺更像...\NIt's more like she --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她給我的感覺就像我喝酒時的感覺\Nit's more like she feels what it was like when I was drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是無法滿足\NWhen I couldn't get enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管我喝多少酒\NNo matter how many drinks I had,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是喝不夠\NI wanted another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想和她在一起\NI -- I don't want to be with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說  我想\NI mean, I -- I -- I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\NBut
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她更像是我女兒\Nit's more like she's my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者我母親\NOr my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道了  太亂了\NI don't know. This is fucked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢說\NTake your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.15,0:08:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不該再跟她聯繫了\NI should cut her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像戒酒一樣\NThe way I did with booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這些  說完了\NThat's all. I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你與我們分享\NThanks for sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要一些時間回答你的問題\NWe'll need some time before responding to your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我願意等\NI could wait as long as necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能要花上一段時間\NIt could take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事關國家安全\NThere are national security matters at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統需要咨詢顧問\NThe vice president needs to consult with his advisors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國家安全\NNational security?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真要用這招嗎  奧利弗\NAre you really gonna play that card, Oliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的回答可能涉及保密信息\NHis answers could entail classified material.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們什麼時候能得到回應\NWhen can we expect a response?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會通知你的\NI'll let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以拿走這些截屏照片嗎\NMay we hold onto the screen cap?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請便\NBe my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會盡快聯繫你  鄧巴女士\NWe'll be in touch soon, Ms. Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統先生\NMr. Vice President?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要認為你這就沒事了\NIf you think you're insulated, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們調查的不止道格拉斯·斯坦普\NOur investigation is much bigger than Douglas Stamper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就到這兒吧  鄧巴女士\NThat's enough, Ms. Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你的配合  副總統先生\NThank you for your time, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意合作\NHappy to cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.74,0:09:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛出虎口  又入狼窩\NFrom the lion's den to a pack of wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是滴血的肉  那就殺了別人\NWhen you're fresh meat, kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給他們更新鮮的肉\Nand throw them something fresher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是菲茨\NHey, I'm Fitz.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格\NDoug.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道  你可以自己硬挺著\NYeah, you know, uh, you can isolate,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獨自承擔這一切\Nwhite-knuckle this shit if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者你也可以向他人求助\NOr you can ask for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有擔保人嗎\NGot a sponsor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  都已經14年了  我沒事\NNo. It's been 14 years. I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話在背面  如果你改主意的話\NNumber's on the back, if you change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你有司機\NThought you had a driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有\NI do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望他聽到什麼\NI didn't want him overhearing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不該來這個州\NYou shouldn't even be near this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在這兒\NI'm not really here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去加州繞了點遠路\NLong layover on my way to California.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稽核員\NI've got auditors,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和聯邦探員都在我辦公室\Nfederal agents in my office,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查看每一份文件和檔案\Ngoing through every file, every document.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們連我的垃圾都翻\NThey're going through my god damn trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她傳喚你就堅持保持沉默\NJust stick to the Fifth if she subpoenas you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們怎麼知道去查斯坦普\NWell, how do they know to look for Stamper?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,專查那天的錄像\NTo search the tapes on that exact day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別亂下結論\NDon't jump to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:10:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是要犧牲我\NYou're throwing me under the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德伍德才是對頭  你不是\NUnderwood's the roadkill. Not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們要坑我\NThey're going to fuck me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們會找到辦法\NThey'll find a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-而且你也知情  -如果是那樣\N- And you know that. - And if that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.49,0:11:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和你的家人會得到妥善安置\Nyou and your family will be taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經給我提供認罪條件了\NThey're already offering me a plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒被起訴呢\NYou haven't even been charged yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我合作的話\NIf I cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能少坐幾年牢\NYou'll do less time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你的家人會一無所有\Nbut your family will have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你出來他們還是一無所有\NThey'll still have nothing when you get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你作證指認雷蒙德\NYou testify against Raymond,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也不會有事  因為他們只有你的證詞作證據\Nand he'll still walk because all they'll have is your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而現在你的證詞沒多少可信度\NAnd that doesn't count for much right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要是不害怕你就不會來了\NYou wouldn't be here if he wasn't afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來不是因為他害怕了\NI'm not here because he's afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你害怕了\NI'm here because you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要確定你不會做蠢事\NAnd I want to make sure you don't do anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在反覆和北京溝通後\NAfter repeated conversations with Beijing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們堅持他們的立場\Nthey remain intractable in their position.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今早命令一個航母戰鬥群\NThis morning I gave orders for a carrier group
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在沖繩海域重新部署\Nto reposition near Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我們的艦隻不會直接\NThis won't put our ships in direct confrontation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和中國軍艦對峙\Nwith the Chinese vessels,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但又能把對方納入航母空襲範圍\Nbut it will put them within reach of airstrikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天晚些時候會知會中國大使\NI'll be informing the Chinese ambassador later today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:12:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會和五角大樓聯合發表聲明\NWe'll release a statement in coordination with the Pentagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  我們的釤儲量\NSir, our stockpiles of samarium
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最多能再堅持兩個月\Nwill only last another two months at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們這麼做\NIf we go this route --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經知道所有人的擔憂\NYeah, I've -- I've heard everyone's concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的決定\NAnd this is the decision I've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有問題嗎\NAny questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  謝謝\NOkay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克\NFrank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行的怎麼樣\NHow'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有些問題需要後續澄清\NWe have a few follow-up questions that we have to address.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如什麼\NLike what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼要緊的\NOh, nothing major.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是零七碎八  一點細節\NJust odds and ends. A few details.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為這調查會簡短而溫和\NI was under the impression this would be short and sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也以為  但她不依不饒\NSo was I, but she's very deliberate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事得盡快平息  弗蘭克\NWe need this over, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少要盡快撇清跟白宮的關係\NAt least as far as the White House is concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能分心\NWe can't be distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是局勢如此緊張的時候\NNot with warships on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我確信馬上就會結束了\NI'm confident we're in the home stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看上去不像嘴上說得那麼輕鬆\NWell, you seem more concerned than you're letting on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  完全沒有\NOh, no, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在搓手\NYou're fidgeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的畢業戒指\NIt's my class ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了我...\NI forget I --
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把它埋了\NI buried it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼\NYou what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說來話長了\NI -- it's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒見過你這麼緊張  弗蘭克\NI've never seen you this stressed before, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒見過您這麼疲憊  先生\NWell, I've never seen you this tired before, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您也有自己的圈\NYou've got rings of your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑眼圈\NDark ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越發明顯了  是嗎\NYeah, they're getting worse, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您該在總統辦公室的沙發上多打打盹\NYou should take more naps on those sofas in the Oval.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今光打盹可管不了用了  弗蘭克\NOh, naps don't cut it these days, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都解不了乏\NNot even a dent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謊話連篇\NLie after lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先是對檢察官  現在是對總統\NFirst to a prosecutor, then to a president.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我全無防護\NI feel exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像我手指上曾被戒指庇護的皮膚\NLike the skin where my ring used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強如阿喀琉斯  也終因踵上一箭斃命\NEven Achilles was only as strong as his heel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格在哪  他老不接電話\NWhere's Doug? He's not answering his phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他去參加互助會了  先生\NHe went to a meeting, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大白天的去幹什麼\NIn the middle of the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他現在可能在往回趕了\NI think he's on his way back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要他趕緊回來\NI want him back now as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  這是給你的\NSir, this arrived for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是雷米跳槽去格蘭頓-希爾時你送給他的手錶\NThe watch you gave Remy when he left for Glendon Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從手錶背面的名言認出來的\NI recognized it from the quote on the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他留信息了嗎\NWas there a message?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  只有這塊表\NNo. Just the watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊聯繫道格\NLet's find Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  先生\NRight away, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你不介意塑料杯子\NForgive the plastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呂克·圖伊曼斯  他有真本事\NLuc Tuymans. He's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就信你了\NWell, I'll take your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我的  這些全都不是\NIt's not mine. None of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在加州  你要是想賣房子\NCalifornia, you want to sell your house,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的房屋中介會先裝修一番\Nyour realtor decorates it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起碼會裝個樣板間\NWell, one room at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算搬到哪去\NWhere you moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在索諾瑪有座小農場\NOh, I have a little ranch in Sonoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妻子離開了\NMy wife's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子也不和我說話\NMy kids won't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少我還有我的畫\NBut at least I'll have my painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:14:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還畫畫嗎\NYou paint?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不畫  農場也是胡扯\NNo. And there's no ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其餘的話  其餘的都是真的\NBut the rest of it -- the rest of it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯\NCheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為傑奎琳·夏普而來\NI'm here about Jacqueline Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在考慮僱用她\NWe're thinking of hiring her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做說客嗎\NA lobbyist?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可能贏不了連任競選了\NShe could lose her re-elect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在局勢對在位者不利\NNot a great time to be an incumbent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你和她關係很近\NI know you two are close.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來是想要什麼\NSo, you're looking for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,推薦函嗎\NA recommendation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是K街員工流動率最低的一家\NWe have the lowest turnover of any shop on K Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}K街上有很多智囊公司  遊說公司和倡導團體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是有原因的\NThere's a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格蘭頓-希爾想用什麼樣的人\NWhat are you looking for at Glendon Hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心狠手辣的人\NA killer instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你找她算是找對人了\NWell, she certainly has that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恕我直言\NForgive me if I'm prying,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不是她造成了你的...\Nbut did she have anything to do with your, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出局\NDeparture?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑姬做了她必須做的事\NJackie did what she had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠不會原諒她\NI'll never forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我理解她為什麼要這麼做\NBut I understand why she did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她究竟做了什麼\NDid what exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我用現金買的票\NI paid cash for my ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非常謹慎\NI was careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顯然不夠謹慎\NClearly not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  賭場裏到處是攝像頭\NSir, the casino had cameras everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本無法避開\NThere was no way to avoid them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他們的監控錄像肯定有幾千小時\NBut there had to have been thousands of hours of footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們怎麼找出來的...\NNow how they found that --
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有個問題我必須要問  道格\NI have to ask you a question, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉  但你要如實作答\NAnd I'm sorry, but I need you to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是又開始酗酒了\NAre you drinking again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒有\NGod no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎\NTruly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想都沒想過\NIt's not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最近的表現可很像喝醉了\NBecause it would explain a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你完全有權生氣\NYou have every right to be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-這是我的錯  -我已經顧不上生氣了\N- This was my fault. - I'm more concerned than I'm upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在需要你  道格\NI need you now, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常需要\NMore than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你我都不年輕了\NWe're not young men.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦失敗  都會老死在牢裏\NIf we fail, we'll die in a cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最近不在狀態\NI haven't been myself lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你14年前也是這麼說的\NThat's what you said to me 14 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我給了你第二次機會  也收穫了回報\NWhen I gave you a second chance, it paid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你戒酒了  道格\NYou got clean, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這份工作是我最看重的  先生  無比重要\NNothing means more to me than this job, sir. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生了什麼\NWhatever's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要知道你能搞定\NI need to know that it can be managed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你需要我的幫助\NAnd if you need my help,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會伸出援手\NI'm here to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事  先生\NI'm good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能解決好  局面會好轉的\NI can handle myself. Things'll be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒給過別人第三次機會\NI've never given someone a third chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在我再給你一次機會\NUntil this very moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非常感激\NAnd I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你後悔的\NYou won't regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請相信這一點  先生\NPlease believe that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是雷米讓他們找到錄像的\NIt was Remy who alerted them to the footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是他的離職禮物\NHis going-away gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讀讀背面\NRead the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得他想傳達什麼信息\NWhat do you think he's trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  找到他  給我安排一次會面\NI don't know, but track him down and set up a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鄧巴那邊怎麼辦\NWhat about Dunbar?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒法逃開事實\NWe can't run from the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我說什麼  我就說什麼\NI'll say whatever you want me to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我負全責\NI'll take responsibility for all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可能會起訴你\NShe could indict you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幕僚就是做這個的\NThat's what having a staff is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有個更好的解決辦法\NI have a better solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我們一起承擔責任  -怎麼做\N- We'll both take responsibility. - How?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後天和鄧巴安排一次會面\NSet up an interview with Dunbar. Day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我們倆需要時間做足準備  -是  先生\N- You and I need time to do our homework. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼時候弄的\NWhen did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密查姆幫我修好了\NMeechum helped me fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:19:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們不讓我跑步  我總得想辦法健身\NIf they're not gonna let me run, I have to work out some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把它搬上樓了\NYou carried it all the way up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更隱秘  有人幫我\NFor privacy. I had help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-密查姆  -沒錯\N- Meechum. - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還真是樣樣通\NWell, he's a jack of all trades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-工匠  搬傢俱的  -肉盾\N- Handyman. Furniture mover. - Human shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有多糟\NHow bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很糟\NBad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們有證據證明道格出現在不該出現的地方\NThey have evidence of Doug being where he shouldn't have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼辦\NWhat are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,講實話\NTell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你該不會真打算...  -不是全部\N- You're not actually gonna -- - Selectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心\NDon't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過絆了一下  還沒摔倒\NIt's a stumble, not a fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是絆一下  你不會這個樣子\NYou aren't like this when it's just a stumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什麼樣子  -你害怕了  我看得出來\N- Like how? - You're scared. I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1分39秒劃五百米  這是我的最佳成績\N500 meters at 1:39. That was my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以此為目標吧\NShoot for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼樣\NHow have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺好\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-藥挺有用的  -那就好\N- The meds are helping. - Oh, that's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐吧\NLet's have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,街角那些人\NThose people at the end of the street...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.47,0:21:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬧得挺厲害\Nit's intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們一天到晚不消停  週末人數還翻番\NThey're there 24/7. Twice as many on the weekends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在都習慣了\NWe're so used to it by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能脫鞋嗎\NCan I take off my shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得該穿得正式點  但我真不喜歡高跟鞋\NI thought I should dress up, but I am not good with heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行  當然可以\NYes. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我媽媽說和裙子很搭\NMy mom said they went with the dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服多了\NMuch better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅根\NLook, Megan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道過去六個月很難熬\NI know the last six months have been difficult,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我需要你的幫助\Nbut I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒能像預想的那樣得到領導層的支持\NWe just don't have the support that we expected in the leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:21:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也猜到你不會只是想問問我的近況\NYeah, I figured this wasn't just about checking up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你之前改過主意  我理解\NYou changed your mind before, and I understand why.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.45,0:22:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在你的情況似乎穩定多了\NBut now it seems as though things are more stable with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.77,0:22:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你願意嗎\NAre you willing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都坐在你家了  說不有點過意不去\NIt's hard to say no when I'm in your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.99,0:22:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也聽到了外頭那些人\NWell, you hear those people out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.05,0:22:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們聲音很響  但我們要發出更高的聲音\NThey're loud, but I think we need to be louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這聲音不能是我的\NAnd it can't be my voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.99,0:22:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我已經是嬰兒殺手  和出軌者\Nbecause I'm the baby killer, the cheater.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音得是你發出的\NIt needs to be your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.34,0:22:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你沒有污點\NA clear voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.63,0:22:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經在軍事法庭上作證了\NI'm already testifying at the court martial.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.69,0:22:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那裏不對媒體開放\NBut that's closed to the media.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠\NIt's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.03,0:22:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事曾發生在很多人身上\NThere are so many people this has happened to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一定是我\NWhy does it have to be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.93,0:22:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是你打來了電話\NBecause you're the one who called.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.60,0:22:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算在麥金尼斯判刑之前發表嗎\NAre you gonna try to put it out before McGinnis gets sentenced?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽斯  有空嗎\NSeth? You have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.52,0:22:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬特  我一會兒打給你\NMatt, I have to call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關門\NClose the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.16,0:23:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統錄用你的時候\NWhen the vice president brought you on board,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是反對的\NI advised against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不得不承認你幹得很好\NBut I can't deny you've done a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.19,0:23:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你這麼說\NI appreciate you saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.19,0:23:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很注重保護副總統\NI'm very protective of the vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.13,0:23:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很難跟旁人分擔這份職責\NI find it hard to share that duty with anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.15,0:23:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也導致我可能出錯\Nwhich leaves me open to error.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的缺點之一\NIt's one of my faults.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.86,0:23:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如我跟副總統說的那樣\NAs I told the vice president,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道信任需要我自己爭取\NI understand that trust is something that I need to earn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我得到工作的途徑不正\NAnd given how I got the job --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果副總統信任你  那我就信任你\NIf the vice president trusts you, then I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.70,0:23:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在是一個團隊\NWe're a team now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.03,0:23:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也沒法孤軍奮戰\NAnd the truth is I can't do this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.53,0:23:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我做任何事都行\NAnything and everything you ask of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能與媒體無關\NIt might have nothing to do with the media.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.22,0:23:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新聞發言人不過是個名號\NPress Secretary is just a title.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.88,0:23:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.84,0:23:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有兩個任務\NWe have two tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.62,0:23:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先  找到雷米·丹頓\NFirst, find me Remy Danton.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.02,0:23:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但要小心\NBut be discreet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.84,0:23:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找他\NI'll track him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.58,0:23:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其次  我要你翻閱副總統的行程記錄\NSecond, I need you to go through the Vice President's travel logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.97,0:23:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去十年的所有記錄\NEverything in the past 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:23:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要找什麼\NWhat are we looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.88,0:24:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何軟肋\NAnything that could hurt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.15,0:24:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從前往後找\NI'll work forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.22,0:24:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你從後往前\NYou work backward.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.21,0:24:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上去辦  還有道格\NI'm on it. And Doug?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.82,0:24:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.78,0:24:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南茜  幫我訂部新手機\NNancy, I need you to order me a new phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.07,0:25:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說是"零七碎八""馬上就會結束"\NYou said "Odds and ends." The "Home stretch."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.71,0:25:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幾個小時前才看到了這些內容\NI was presented with this information just hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.91,0:25:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是能招致彈劾的罪行  弗蘭克\NWe're talking about impeachable offenses, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.56,0:25:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不會  先生\NNot at all, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.49,0:25:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的幕僚長...\NYour Chief of Staff was --
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.52,0:25:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時覺得賭場跟這事有關\NI had a gut feeling that the casino was involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.36,0:25:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我派道格去查了\NI sent Doug down there to get to the bottom of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.07,0:25:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一發現聯繫就該馬上去找司法部\NYou should have taken this to the DOJ the first inkling you had --
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.29,0:25:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時就不想那麼做\NThat's exactly what I didn't want.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.36,0:25:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一沒有什麼  我卻製造事端\NTo create some ruckus if nothing was going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.44,0:25:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能私自調查  弗蘭克\NYou can't go on conducting your own investigations, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.41,0:25:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查明真相  盡職調查  隨您怎麼說\NFact-finding, due diligence, whatever you want to call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.46,0:25:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有任何違法行為  我必須知道\NIf any laws were being broken, I wanted to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.94,0:25:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就要這麼跟鄧巴說嗎\NAnd that's what you want to tell Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.08,0:25:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想透露我們的外交手段\NThat I didn't want to disclose our diplomatic protocols.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.48,0:26:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心中期選舉\NThat I was concerned about the midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.20,0:26:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想保護美國總統\NAnd that I wanted to protect the President of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.06,0:26:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許我做得不對\NNow, maybe what I did was wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.88,0:26:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我沒幹任何違法的事\Nbut I didn't do anything illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.69,0:26:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你確定\NYou certain of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.37,0:26:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟我的律師認真探討過了\NI've discussed this at length with my lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.55,0:26:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使我們承認這一切\NDunbar does not strike me as the sort of person
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.34,0:26:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得鄧巴也不會就此打住\Nwho will put on the brakes, even if we admit all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.55,0:26:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反而還可能促使她繼續深挖\NIn fact, it might encourage her to dig deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.94,0:26:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得對\NYou're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.17,0:26:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我打算上交我全部的行程記錄\NWhich is why I want to hand over all of my travel logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.20,0:26:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得您也該這麼做\NAnd I think you should, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.34,0:26:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自願上交嗎\NVolunteer them?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.54,0:26:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  表示我們樂意合作\NYeah. As a gesture of cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.12,0:26:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們表示做得夠多了\NHaven't we made enough gestures?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.77,0:26:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣她就不會那麼叫勁了\NThat'll take the wind outta her sails.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.29,0:26:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不想讓她\NNo. I don't, uh, want her,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.47,0:26:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔細查看我所有的行蹤\Nuh, poring over every one of my comings and goings.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.40,0:26:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是在擔心他的婚姻咨詢\NHe's worried about his marriage counseling,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.96,0:26:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也該擔心\Nas he should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.66,0:26:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果您是在擔心您的婚姻咨詢\NIf you're worried about your marriage counseling,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.29,0:26:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您不必擔心\Nyou shouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.12,0:26:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被外界知道  會造成多大影響\NImagine the fallout if the public were to find out that --
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.10,0:26:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是大海裏的一根針\NA needle in a haystack,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.04,0:26:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不是鄧巴要找的那根\Nand not a needle that Dunbar is looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.87,0:26:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已經會見了一半的國會議員\NShe's interviewed half of Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.00,0:26:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這女人是要見血\NThat woman's after blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.04,0:26:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是八卦\NBut not for gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.33,0:26:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算她真的起疑了\NAnd even if she does raise an eyebrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.98,0:26:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您只是去探望一位生病的朋友  不是嗎\Nyou were visiting a sick friend, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.00,0:27:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  表面上是這樣\NYeah, ostensibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.96,0:27:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這她沒什麼可說的\NWell, she couldn't possibly find any fault with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.35,0:27:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫嘉利克過來\NI'd like Galich in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.61,0:27:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不打擾了\NI'll let you two talk privately.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.05,0:27:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候去見鄧巴\NWhen are you seeing Dunbar?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.40,0:27:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天  這樣您也有時間準備\NTomorrow, so you have some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.08,0:27:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會跟比爾談談  回頭找你\NWell, I'll speak to Bill and get back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.45,0:27:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他會建議您不要這麼做  這是他職責所在\NHe'll advise you against it, which is his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.20,0:27:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我會強烈建議您想想政治而不是法律\NBut I would just encourage you to think politics and not legalese.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.25,0:27:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  先生\NThank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.67,0:27:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,議員女士\NCongresswoman?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.78,0:27:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼要投票給你\NWhy should I vote for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.50,0:27:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  馬克\NIt's -- it's okay, Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.80,0:27:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安\NGoodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.96,0:27:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來很疲憊\NYou look tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.49,0:27:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忙了一天競選嗎\NLong day on the campaign trail?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.72,0:27:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這幹什麼\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.46,0:27:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒跟我說過哈維梅耶女兒的事\NYou never told me about Havemeyer's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.55,0:27:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道\NEveryone knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.90,0:27:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全世界都知道\NThe whole world knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.72,0:27:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不知道你常去探望她\NBut not that you visited her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.72,0:27:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是你洩露出去的\NThat you leaked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.40,0:28:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你大老遠跑來加州就是為了問我這些\NYou came all the way to California to ask me about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.44,0:28:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是到了加州才知道的\NI came to California to find out about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.52,0:28:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我提出買下哈維梅耶的房子\NI offered to buy Havemeyer's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.06,0:28:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他就那麼告訴我了\Nbut he told me for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.76,0:28:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說得對\NYou were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.19,0:28:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我確實忙了一天競選\NIt has been a long day on the trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.27,0:28:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不相上下\NIt's still a close race.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.80,0:28:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是選民知道你是怎麼當上黨鞭就不會了\NBut not if the voters know how you became whip.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.90,0:28:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是在威脅我嗎\NAre you honestly threatening me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.39,0:28:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安排和弗蘭克的會面\NSet up a meeting with Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.37,0:28:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎你怎麼說\NI don't care what you talk about,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.26,0:28:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是你單獨一人  會面也有記錄就行\Nlong as you're alone and the meeting is on the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.30,0:28:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後你去和鄧巴談\NThen you're gonna sit down with Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.82,0:28:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已經問完我了\NI've already done my interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.10,0:28:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴她  是弗蘭克逼你那麼說的\NTell her Frank grilled you on your testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.13,0:28:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作偽證嗎\NPerjure myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.37,0:28:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保住你的位子\NSave your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.46,0:28:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說出去吧\NYou know what? Tell everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.84,0:28:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想那會有什麼後果\NThink how that'd play out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.61,0:28:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎\NI don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.71,0:28:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真要為了弗蘭克毀了自己嗎\NYou'd really toss yourself off a cliff for Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.54,0:28:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不效忠於弗蘭克·安德伍德\NI have zero allegiance for Frank Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.32,0:28:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會受他操縱\NI won't be manipulated by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.96,0:29:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更不會被你操縱\NAnd I sure as fuck won't be manipulated by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.35,0:29:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是虛張聲勢\NI'm not bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.84,0:29:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就是對的\NThen I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.81,0:29:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於什麼\NAbout what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.66,0:29:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不在乎我\NHow little I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.82,0:29:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那跟這個沒關係\NThat has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.03,0:29:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然有關係\NIt has everything to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.23,0:29:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該覺得噁心  但我沒有\NI should feel disgusted, but I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.66,0:29:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是特別失望\NJust supremely disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.22,0:29:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們十分鐘前接到電話\NWe got the call 10 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.27,0:29:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接從白宮顧問那裏打來的\NDirect from the White House counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.84,0:29:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統要上交一切嗎\NThe President's turning over everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.24,0:29:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從他就職那天開始\NFrom the day he took office.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.33,0:29:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會包括他去拜訪那位朋友嗎\NAnd we're sure this includes the visits to his friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.06,0:29:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然  安保人員全部出動\NIt has to. It was full security detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.51,0:29:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天啊\NPhenomenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.47,0:29:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有下手的地方了\NWe have something we can work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.18,0:29:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於我的記錄...\NNow, as for my logs...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.50,0:29:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有問題\NThey're clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.68,0:29:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿生命打包票嗎\NYou'd bet your life on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.42,0:29:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\NI would.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.38,0:29:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  先生\NMe, too, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.71,0:30:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經檢查了兩次  反覆檢查\NWe've been through 'em twice, backward and forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.74,0:30:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的聲明呢\NMy statement?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.92,0:30:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你的收件箱裏\NIn your inbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.12,0:30:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看過了  塞斯幹得很漂亮\NI looked it over. Seth did a nice job.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.72,0:30:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會面一結束我們就要把消息發佈出去\NWe need to go wide with this the moment the interview's over,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.59,0:30:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣鄧巴如果打算發佈什麼消息\Nso that we beat Dunbar to the punch
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.89,0:30:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以先發制人\Nin case she decides to release something.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.65,0:30:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會守在電腦前\NI'll be at my computer,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.39,0:30:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一收到道格的消息就按下"發送"鍵\Nready to press "Send" the moment I hear from Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.21,0:30:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆睡過覺嗎\NHave either of you slept?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.42,0:30:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們很清醒  全速運轉\NWe're awake. Fully operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.83,0:30:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去洗個澡  換件衣服\NYou take a shower and put on a fresh suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.00,0:30:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  先生  我們在那邊見\NYes, sir. I'll see you over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.80,0:30:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有至少三小時\NYou have at least three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.97,0:30:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打個盹吧  去我辦公室睡\NTake a nap. You can use my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.80,0:30:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你作證的時候麥金尼斯將軍就在法庭裏\NGeneral McGinnis was in the courtroom when you testified.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.48,0:30:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.90,0:30:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你私下見過他嗎\NHad you seen him in person --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.92,0:30:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在他侵犯你之後\NI mean, since he assaulted you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.65,0:30:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.19,0:30:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼感覺\NSo what was that like?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.56,0:30:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愉快\NNot fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.63,0:30:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼個不愉快\NNot fun how?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.57,0:30:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很難受  真的很難受\NIt was hard. Really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.63,0:30:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著  梅根\NLook, Megan,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.24,0:31:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我同意把文章的焦點轉移到你身上\NI -- I agreed to change the focus of my piece to focus on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.67,0:31:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道這肯定很難\Nand, you know, I know this has gotta be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.61,0:31:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你得幫幫我\NI need you to help me out a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.71,0:31:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.72,0:31:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很擅長這個  我很緊張\NI'm not very good at this. I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.33,0:31:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打電話去安德伍德夫人的訪談時挺好的\NYou seemed fine when you called into Mrs. Underwood's interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.74,0:31:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在電話那頭跟我在一起\NShe was there with me on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.14,0:31:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的緊張情緒\NYour nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.50,0:31:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道自你被侵犯後  這一直是個問題\NI know that's been an issue since the assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.04,0:31:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種防禦心理\NThe defense brought up
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.83,0:31:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引起了情緒與精神的不穩定\Nwhat they called emotional and mental instability.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.85,0:31:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是那樣\NThat's what always happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.18,0:31:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被攻擊的人會再次被攻擊\NThe person who was attacked gets attacked all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.80,0:31:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼感覺\NHow did that make you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.33,0:31:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我覺得憤怒\NIt made me angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.10,0:31:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,律師一直問我恐慌癥的事\NThe lawyer kept coming after me about my panic attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.81,0:31:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我的抗抑鬱藥\Nmy antidepressants.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.79,0:31:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我只是緊緊盯著麥金尼斯\NBut I just kept staring at McGinnis.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.09,0:31:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓他知道我能承受\NI wanted him to see I could take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.00,0:31:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很堅強\NThat I was strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.07,0:31:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓他先轉過臉去\NI wanted to make him look away first.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.89,0:31:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有嗎\NAnd did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.40,0:31:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  當我說到他不只是侵犯了我的身體\NYes. When I said he did more than violate my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.93,0:31:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還背叛了自己的國家\NHe betrayed his country.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.99,0:31:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毀了海軍陸戰隊的聲譽\NHe robbed it of a good Marine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.82,0:32:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們談談國會正在談論的\NLet's talk about the Sexual Assault Bill
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.26,0:32:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,性侵法案吧\Nthat's in front of Congress right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.46,0:32:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人提出了很強烈的反對意見\NYou know it's taken some significant opposition,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.60,0:32:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是另一個老兵\Nmost notably from another veteran,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.39,0:32:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑奎琳·夏普\NJacqueline Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.93,0:32:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我說  她也背叛了自己的國家\NIf you ask me, she's betraying her country, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.57,0:32:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鄧巴女士\NMs. Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.96,0:32:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統先生\NMr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.61,0:32:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你多給我們幾天時間\NThank you for giving us a few extra days.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.54,0:32:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耐心對我來說不是問題\NI have no problem being patient,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.54,0:32:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能因此得到坦率的回答\Nas long as it leads to forthright answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.55,0:32:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你繼續等待了\NWell, I won't make you wait a moment longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.88,0:32:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以開始了嗎\NShall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.32,0:32:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找到這裏了\NOh, you found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.37,0:32:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請坐\NHave a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.94,0:32:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們馬上就完事了\NWe're just finishing up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.19,0:32:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得怎麼樣  塔斯克先生\NWhat do you think, Mr. Tusk?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.08,0:32:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留著還是剃了\NKeep growing it or have it shaved?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.00,0:32:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是留著吧\NAh, I guess I'll keep growing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.51,0:32:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題\NAh, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.29,0:32:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把後面清理一下\NLet me just clean up the back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.60,0:32:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不了  麥克  讓我們單獨待會兒\NNo, Mack, if you'd give me a couple of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.74,0:32:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝了\NAppreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.42,0:32:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概十年前我在這裏建造了這個地方\NI had this place built down here about 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.37,0:32:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我厭倦了每兩周都要開車穿過整個城市\NI got tired of driving all the way across town every two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.12,0:33:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在坐個電梯就到了\NNow it's just an elevator ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.88,0:33:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真方便\NConvenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.96,0:33:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道不方便的是什麼嗎\NYou know what isn't convenient?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.65,0:33:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我辦公室裏擠下八個律師\NCramming eight attorneys into my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.59,0:33:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裏不是為召集我律所所有合夥人準備的\NIt was not designed for the entire partnership of my law firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.57,0:33:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們比較擔心拉尼根\NThey're worried about Lanagin.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.63,0:33:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有點害怕  但他能挺住\NHe's a little shaky, but he'll hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.83,0:33:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德伍德\NUnderwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.87,0:33:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博奇出手了\NBirch delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.05,0:33:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鄧巴提出斯坦普的問題了吧\NAnd did Dunbar bring up Stamper?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.17,0:33:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會面是閉門的\NThe sessions are closed-door,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.46,0:33:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我想她肯定會提的\Nbut I can't imagine she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.92,0:33:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可憐的哈維梅耶那邊呢\NAnd what about poor Havemeyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.47,0:33:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在傑姬·夏普的事上對我們有幫助嗎\NWas he any help to us on Jackie Sharp?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.54,0:33:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的猶豫說明進展不順吧\NI do not take your hesitation as a promising sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.31,0:33:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向來不喜歡讓你失望\NI never like disappointing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.34,0:33:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他什麼都不知道嗎\NHe had nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.50,0:33:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.98,0:33:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得他是確實不知道呢\NNow, do you think that's because there's nothing here,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.53,0:33:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是他在保護她呢\Nor because he's protecting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.13,0:33:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是不知道\NThere's nothing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.98,0:33:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以再找一個別的議員\NI can go to another congressman --
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.04,0:33:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行\NNo, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.08,0:34:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須是個曝光率高的人\NIt has to be somebody high-profile,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.09,0:34:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領導層的人  才能引起轟動\Nsomeone in the leadership who will make waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.72,0:34:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我再找找博奇\NLet me get back to Birch.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.78,0:34:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太明顯了\NToo obvious,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.41,0:34:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然他擺明了不會對弗蘭克手軟\Nnow that he's shown no sympathy for Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.47,0:34:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算盤不能打得太響\NThis can't look orchestrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.59,0:34:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多線作戰  雷米\NMultiple fronts, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.69,0:34:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須得是傑姬·夏普\NHas to be Jackie Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.40,0:34:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麥克\NMack?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.44,0:34:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把頭髮弄完吧\NLet's finish up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.53,0:34:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得回去幹活兒了\NI gotta get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.73,0:34:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  老闆\NYou got it, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.70,0:34:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也得去幹活兒了\NYou need to get back to work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.01,0:34:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們說的事\NAnd what we discussed?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.57,0:34:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它們辦成\NMake it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.00,0:34:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你之前否認你是去私下接觸的人\NYou denied being a back channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.47,0:34:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒否認\NI did not deny.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.67,0:34:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有證實  因為這是機密信息\NI chose not to confirm because it was classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.75,0:34:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你的辦公室一直否認\NBut your office has consistently denied --
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.33,0:34:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讓道格那麼做的\NI instructed Doug to do so,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.51,0:34:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有我的新聞部\Nalong with my communications department.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.56,0:34:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,私下接觸如果公之於眾\NWhen a back channel becomes public,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.43,0:34:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就沒什麼用了\Nit defeats its purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.75,0:34:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精心編造的謊言\NAn orchestrated deception --
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.13,0:34:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們不予置評\NIf we had refused to comment,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.45,0:34:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們就會知道確有其事\Nit would have suggested that it was true,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.01,0:34:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會危及這一渠道\Nwhich would have endangered the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.62,0:34:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我實在沒辦法\NI really had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.78,0:34:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馮先生目前在迪拜\NMr. Feng is currently in Dubai.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.47,0:34:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.02,0:34:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他因腐敗指控畏罪潛逃\NHe's fleeing corruption charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.15,0:34:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是他第一次被指控了\NNot the first time he's been accused.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.01,0:34:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的問題是什麼呢\NAnd your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.58,0:35:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道是他洗錢  副總統先生\NI know he laundered the money, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.18,0:35:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到確鑿證據\NIt's just a matter of time
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.30,0:35:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是遲早的事\Nbefore I have the proof to substantiate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.89,0:35:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我的問題就是  我再問一遍\NSo my question, which I am asking again,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.21,0:35:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當時是否知情\Nis whether you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.50,0:35:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就再回答一遍\NAnd I will repeat my answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.18,0:35:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時並不知情\NI did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.41,0:35:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時的確覺得有點不對勁\NI did sense that something was awry,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.68,0:35:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格知道我的擔憂\Nand Doug was aware of my concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.70,0:35:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得調查清楚是我的責任\NAnd I took it upon myself to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.85,0:35:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統並不知情\NThe vice president didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.31,0:35:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道他去賭場的事嗎\NYou had no knowledge he was going to the casino?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.45,0:35:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  但這並不代表\NNone. But that doesn't mean
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.91,0:35:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不對我手下的行為負責\NI don't take full responsibility for my staff's behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.05,0:35:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我責無旁貸\NThe buck stops with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.16,0:35:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你發現了什麼\NAnd what did you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.42,0:35:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒發現  沒有非法行為\NNothing. No illegal activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.68,0:35:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不像你那麼神通廣大\NI don't have the same resources that you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.24,0:35:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有所懷疑\NIf you suspected,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.14,0:35:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不立即聯絡國家印第安人博彩委員會\Nwhy didn't you go immediately to the NIGC,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.42,0:35:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,印第安人事務局  或者...\Nthe BIA, the Department --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.74,0:35:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得理解\NYou have to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.72,0:35:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們中期選舉很吃力\NWe're facing very difficult midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.69,0:35:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想為一些\NI didn't want to bring attention
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.79,0:35:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有實據的判斷而引發關注\Nto a series of allegations that may have no basis in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.66,0:35:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許這邏輯不是很合理\NNow, that may have been misguided logic,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.47,0:35:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這是我當時的選擇\Nbut that's how I chose to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.88,0:35:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錯誤全在我一個人頭上\NThe mistake is mine and mine alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.21,0:35:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟道格沒關係\NNot Doug's.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.88,0:35:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然更算不到總統頭上\NAnd certainly not the president's.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.28,0:35:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要是說我覺得\NIt shouldn't surprise you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.14,0:36:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒看到事情的全部  你不會意外吧\Nif I say it feels like I am not getting the full picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.53,0:36:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我打算把全部展示給你\NWhich is why I'm prepared to give you the full picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.11,0:36:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧利弗\NOliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.55,0:36:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白宮相信透明度\NThe White House believes in transparency.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.05,0:36:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統全部個人出行記錄\NAll of the vice president's personal travel logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.05,0:36:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還包括我十年黨鞭任期內的記錄\NAnd the last 10 years since I became whip.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.73,0:36:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和總統就職後的所有記錄\NAs well as the president's since inauguration.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.43,0:36:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會面的對象和時間都沒有任何問題\NThere should be no doubt as to whom we met with and when.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.97,0:36:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很懷疑裏面的內容\NI am skeptical about what this contains.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.54,0:36:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點我們也預料到了\NWhich is what we anticipated
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.99,0:36:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以奧利弗會全程在場\Nand why Oliver will walk you through anything
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.23,0:36:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪你審查全部材料\Nyou might need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.39,0:36:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都在那兒了\NIt's all there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.53,0:36:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你還有其他疑問或要求\NBut if you have any questions or requests,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.44,0:36:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也願意傾力協助\Nwe'll be happy to facilitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.16,0:36:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始我很緊張\NI mean, at first I was really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.39,0:36:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我一進入狀態\NBut then as soon as I started getting into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.64,0:36:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始吐露心聲\Nstarting speaking from my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.19,0:36:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都自然脫口而出\Nall these things poured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.80,0:36:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些我一度想說的\NEverything I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.26,0:36:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想說的都說出來了\NThat I've been wanting to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.13,0:36:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽斯告訴我馬特很滿意\NSeth told me that Matt was very impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.44,0:36:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想做更多\NI want to do more.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.43,0:36:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做更多採訪\NMore interviews?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.51,0:36:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報刊採訪  上電視\NArticles. TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.86,0:37:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論什麼都可以\NWhatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.29,0:37:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想幫忙\NI want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.19,0:37:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這很好  梅根\NThat's great, Megan.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.95,0:37:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你給我這個機會\NThank you for making me do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.69,0:37:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這對我來說是邁了一大步\NIt was a big step for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.79,0:37:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還要趕飛機\NYou have a plane to catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.98,0:37:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你需要我做別的採訪  我可以留下\NI can stay longer, if you need me to do another.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.24,0:37:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如你先回芝加哥\NWhy don't you head back to Chicago,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.87,0:37:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我們制定好計劃\Nand as soon as we put a plan together
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.85,0:37:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再給你打電話\Nwe can give you a buzz?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.35,0:37:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能喝杯水嗎\NCan I get a glass of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.95,0:37:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自來水  還是瓶裝的\NTap is fine, or you want bottled --
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.51,0:37:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己來\NI can get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.51,0:37:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漢納希女士的車準備好了  夫人\NWe've got Ms. Hennessey's car ready, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.47,0:37:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾德華\NEdward?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.62,0:37:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去機場接她時\NDid she seem all right
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.56,0:37:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她看起來還好嗎\Nwhen you picked her up from the airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.22,0:37:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您的意思是\NHow do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.92,0:37:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不確定  正常嗎\NI don't know. Normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.23,0:37:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  可以這麼說\NYes. I'd say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.56,0:37:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她情緒起伏很大\NShe's very up and down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.18,0:37:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反覆無常  容易激動\NVery skittish and manic.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.70,0:37:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她確實有點緊張\NI guess she did seem nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.41,0:37:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒怎麼交流\NWe didn't talk much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.99,0:37:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看她\NI'll get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.59,0:37:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在外面等\NI'll be outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.94,0:37:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅根\NMegan?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.57,0:38:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己來\NI've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.15,0:38:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的\NReally.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.08,0:38:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事\NI'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.41,0:38:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,車在外面等著了\NThe car is ready whenever you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.10,0:38:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你\NThank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.22,0:38:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一路順風  保持聯繫\NHave a safe flight. I'll be in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.26,0:39:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我與鄧巴女士的談話卓有成效\NI just had a very productive interview with Ms. Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.38,0:39:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發新聞稿\NSend out the press release.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.56,0:39:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.30,0:39:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您還好嗎  夫人\NYou okay, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.17,0:39:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事  我只是打碎了\NOh, I'm fine. I just dropped...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.74,0:39:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我來\NPlease, let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.87,0:39:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  我可以的\NOh, uh, it's fine. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.33,0:39:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我來  您光著腳\NNo, I've got it. You're barefoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.52,0:39:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾德華  真的  沒事的\NEdward, you don't have to. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.56,0:39:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊  怎麼了\NOh, no. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.56,0:39:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死\NDamn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.87,0:39:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找繃帶\NLet me get some bandages.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.09,0:39:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了\NYou don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.86,0:39:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我堅持  別動\NNo, I want to. Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.36,0:39:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前的報導都是正面的\NThe coverage has been mostly positive so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.55,0:39:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鄧巴那邊呢\NDunbar's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.00,0:39:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們只說很期待對記錄的審核\NAll they've said is they look forward to reviewing the logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.41,0:40:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人提到道格嗎\NAny heat on Doug?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.84,0:40:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一些\NSome.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.77,0:40:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多人要求我發表評論\NI'm getting a lot of requests for comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.06,0:40:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的個人行動\NI acted on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.45,0:40:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會全力配合司法部\NAnd I will fully cooperate with the Justice Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.05,0:40:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以這麼對外說嗎\NWe can put that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.85,0:40:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生\NSir?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.94,0:40:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這或許會吸引更多注意\NIt might generate more interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.09,0:40:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意我  而不是副總統\NOn me. Not the vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.66,0:40:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼情況我都能應付好\NI can handle whatever comes my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.42,0:40:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼說\NPut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.09,0:40:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去把最新的剪報都打出來  先生\NI'll print you out the most recent clips, too, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.63,0:40:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要想辦法向鄧巴透露風聲嗎\NShould I find a way to tip off Dunbar?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.82,0:40:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是順其自然吧\NLet nature take its course.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.03,0:40:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛找到雷米\NWe got a hold of Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.06,0:40:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他剛回來了\NHe just got back to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.04,0:40:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪\NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.89,0:40:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你的安保隊都安排好了\NI've arranged everything with your detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.26,0:40:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做得很好  道格\NYou've done good work, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.05,0:40:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  先生\NThank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.59,0:41:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  這樣好多了\NThere. That's much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.60,0:41:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  夫人\NThanks, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.37,0:41:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了\NI'm gonna get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.29,0:41:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我有點喝醉了\NI'm sorry I'm a little drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.65,0:42:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是您家  您可以隨心所欲\NIt's your house. You do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.34,0:42:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也該喝一杯酒\NYou should have a glass of wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.04,0:42:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  夫人  但是...\NI appreciate that, ma'am, but --
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.55,0:42:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已經下班了  對嗎\NYou're off your shift, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.49,0:42:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  沒錯\NI am. That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.04,0:42:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不許說不喝\NThen I won't take no for an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.61,0:42:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您不該把好東西浪費在我身上\NUh, you shouldn't waste any of your good stuff on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.79,0:42:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我其實根本不懂品酒\NI don't really know anything about wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.59,0:42:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那喝點波本威士忌怎麼樣\NThen how about bourbon?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.14,0:42:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定想喝一點\NI bet you like a little of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.16,0:42:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當然不介意能喝點波本威士忌\NI definitely don't mind a bourbon from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.73,0:42:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就喝波本威士忌\NThen bourbon it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.34,0:42:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在很難找啊\NYou're a tough man to track down these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.93,0:42:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿到手錶了\NYou got the watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.42,0:42:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變則善\N"To improve is to change."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.46,0:42:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,常變則至善\N"To perfect is to change often."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.99,0:42:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你想要什麼樣的變化呢\NWhat sort of change are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.18,0:43:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我有選擇餘地的變化\NWhichever leaves me options.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.86,0:43:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在格蘭頓-希爾遇到麻煩了\NTrouble at Glendon Hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.66,0:43:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶薪休假  直到調查結束\NPaid leave till the investigation is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.29,0:43:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少是帶薪的\NWell, at least you're being paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.21,0:43:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是終止我合夥人身份的第一步\NFirst step in terminating my partnership.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.38,0:43:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事你也懂\NYou know how things go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.41,0:43:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什麼\NNo matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.46,0:43:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這都是我洗不掉的污點\Nthere's a stain I can't wash out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.94,0:43:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你在尋找就業機會嘍\NSo you're looking for career opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.90,0:43:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是要把自己整個賣給你\NI'm not offering myself to you wholesale.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.01,0:43:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會繼續跟你鬥  但是力度會小一點\NI keep fighting you, but I can fight you less.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.39,0:43:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說"小一點"的意思是...\NAnd by "less" you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.10,0:43:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你痛  但不會讓你完蛋\NEnough to hurt, but not finish you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.54,0:43:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為回報  我在格蘭頓-希爾之外也有前途\NAnd in return I have a future beyond Glendon Hill,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.99,0:43:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什麼樣的前途\Nwhatever that might look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.18,0:43:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你是要保持中立\NSo you offer neutrality,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.64,0:43:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但最終會追隨勝利者\Nbut you'll go with the victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.76,0:43:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看著更厲害的人獲勝\NI figure let the best man win.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.07,0:43:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你失敗了\NAnd if you go down,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.87,0:43:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會是因為我\Nit won't be because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.11,0:43:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這已經挺夠意思了\NThat's worth something.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.66,0:43:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是為什麼\NWhere is this coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.69,0:43:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保險  沒別的\NInsurance. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.70,0:43:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這跟傑姬有關嗎\NDoes it have anything to do with Jackie?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.90,0:44:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經結束了\NThat's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.07,0:44:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你已經收服了博奇\NI know you've got Birch in your pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.68,0:44:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不會選擇烏麥克  我們太親密了\NWomack's not an option. We're too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.62,0:44:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是傑奎琳\NBut Jacqueline...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.95,0:44:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這單純是關於我的前途\NThis is about my future, pure and simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.59,0:44:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟她沒關係\NShe's not a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.26,0:44:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留著這塊表吧  就當做誠意的象徵\NKeep the watch, as a token of good faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.18,0:44:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他雖然否認  但他在保護她\NHe might deny it, but he's protecting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.01,0:44:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他沒有意識到的是\NWhat he doesn't realize is
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.44,0:44:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我比雷蒙德更不在乎傑姬\NI have even less regard for Jackie than Raymond does.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.76,0:44:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的雷米\NPoor Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.19,0:44:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感情用事\NThe heart can choke the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.65,0:44:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理智就會受到影響\Nwhen all its blood flows back unto itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.39,0:45:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說"我不喜歡深色頭髮的女孩"\NHe said, "I don't like brunettes."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.61,0:45:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我差點錯過了派對\NLooks like I almost missed the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.59,0:45:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經下班了  先生\NI'm off the clock, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.76,0:45:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別緊張  弗蘭西斯  我打破了一個杯子\NOh, relax. Francis, I broke a glass,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.61,0:46:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾德華被一塊碎片割傷了手\Nand Edward cut his hand on a piece of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.82,0:46:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天吶\NJesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.75,0:46:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得給你換繃帶了\NI have to change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.94,0:46:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那個解下來  我去拿新的...\NTake that off, and I'll get fresh...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.96,0:46:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望您不要介意  先生\NI hope you don't mind, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.08,0:46:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我下了班...\NI was off-duty --
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.96,0:46:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是不是...\NIs she, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.06,0:46:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝醉了嗎  有一點\NDrunk? A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.85,0:46:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喝了多少這東西\NHow many of these have you had?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.01,0:46:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝了一點\NA few.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.72,0:46:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不止一點吧\NMore than a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.47,0:46:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以用你的杯子嗎\NMay I?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.83,0:46:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用吧\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.80,0:46:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看\NLet me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.00,0:46:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼事\NOh, it's not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.96,0:46:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流了很多血\NThere's a lot of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.31,0:46:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有看上去那麼糟\NLooks worse than it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.16,0:47:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛嗎\NIs it painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.68,0:47:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝了酒不那麼痛了\NThe bourbon helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.49,0:47:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果痛你就說\NNow you let me know if this hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.17,0:47:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不痛  先生\NNot one bit, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.97,0:49:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你頭痛嗎\NHow's your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.96,0:49:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事\NFine.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.00,0:50:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡前吃了幾片阿司匹林\NTook a few aspirin before I went to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.63,0:50:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢\NYou?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.80,0:50:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我睡得可香了\NI slept like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.43,0:50:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好  你需要好好睡一覺\NGood. You needed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.78,0:50:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.54,0:50:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪\NSomething weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.57,0:50:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有個地址老是出現\NThis one address keeps popping up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.05,0:50:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德伍德嗎\NUnderwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.82,0:50:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統\NThe president.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.69,0:50:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  密查姆\NMorning, Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.90,0:50:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  副總統先生\NMorning, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.60,0:50:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是美好的一天\NIt's a beautiful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.44,0:51:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}{\pos(193,145)}當美國政府爆出醜聞  需要進行徹底調查時\N為了避免司法部的調查偏向現政府\N國會會要求司法部任命特別檢察官  進行全權獨立的調查\N特別檢察官的人選必須是不擔任政府公職的人員\N美國歷史上最著名的特別檢察官\N當屬哈佛大學法學教授阿奇伯德·考克斯\N1973年5月  考克斯被任命為負責調查水門事件的特別檢察官\N在調查過程中發現總統尼克松有違法嫌疑\N尼克松遂命令司法部長解除考克斯的職務\N但是當時連續兩名司法部長都拒絕了總統的要求\N並辭職抗議  考克斯最終還是被尼克松政府解職\N但是他仍然被認為在水門事件中發揮了非常重要的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.44,0:52:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}{\pos(193,145)}克林頓擔任總統期間  在白水事件和萊溫斯基醜聞爆發後\N肯·斯塔爾被任命為特別檢察官  調查克林頓一系列的醜聞\N在他的努力下  國會啟動了對克林頓的彈劾程序\N但是最終因為沒有獲得足夠票數  彈劾沒有成功\N斯塔爾在克林頓醜聞期間也成為全美知名的政治人物
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.44,0:52:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}{\pos(193,145)}美國法律規定  只有公民才能在政治活動或選舉中進行捐贈\N持有綠卡者也可以參加政治選舉活動進行助選\N但除此之外  外國公民  包括在美國持有合法簽證者\N都不能進行政治捐贈\N最高法院對超級政治行動委員會做出裁定後\N由於一些對超級政治行動委員會的捐款難以確定來源\N一些政治組織也不對外公佈捐助者的身份\N所以在2012年美國總統大選中  很多媒體質疑\N會不會有外國政治獻金通過超級政治行動委員會\N對特定候選人進行捐款  但是目前看  在大型的選舉中\N尚沒有發現有確定的大額外國捐款者\N本劇中的情節在現實中出現的可能性不大\N2012年1月  美國最高法院在一項判決中\N重新確認了不允許外國資金資助選舉的禁令
